snippet.textDisplay: Hey SupraDarky. I wanted to say thanks. The day before you uploaded this song, I subscribed to you. I watched this video and immediately fell in love. This led me to buy the game online right on the spot just for the music. I played it to the end and now it's one of my most favorite RPGs. It was a great game and it's funny to me that if you didn't decide to upload this video, I wouldn't have been able to experience a story and OST so beautiful and grand. So thank you!
